  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/py-evm/pull/869 introduces a new `validate_header_response` helper to ensure that a peer did indeed return a valid response to the requested headers.\r\n\r\nthis validation is currently only applied in the dao-fork checks.  It should be allied to all places where headers are requested.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nThis validation should be applied to the following places.\r\n\r\n- Need to pass the request params into `_process_headers` here: https://github.com/ethereum/py-evm/blob/master/p2p/chain.py#L168-L184\r\n- Add validation in fast sync: https://github.com/ethereum/py-evm/blob/master/p2p/chain.py#L220-L230\r\n- Add validation in regular sync: https://github.com/ethereum/py-evm/blob/master/p2p/chain.py#L566-L578\r\n",
